<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-03-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-03-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="165" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d165">
                        <head><persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Burnley</persName></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi></placeName>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-03-14"><hi rend="italic">March</hi> 14, 1865.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                            receipt of your note of the 7th instant, enclosing a copy of a despatch
                            from his excellency the governor general of Canada, in regard to the
                            steps taken by the authorities under his control to guard against the
                            steamer Georgiana getting into the hands of parties hostile to the
                            United States.</p>
                        <p>I will thank you to express to his excellency the satisfaction with which
                            this government views his prompt and friendly action in the matter.</p>
                        <p>I have the honor to be, with the highest consideration, sir, your
                            obedient servant,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed></closer>
                        <postscript>
                            <p>J. <hi rend="smallcaps">Hume Burnley,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c</hi>.</p>
                        </postscript>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>